@startuml Deployment Diagram

skinparam node {
  BackgroundColor<<netlify>> #10b981
  BackgroundColor<<render>> #3b82f6
  BackgroundColor<<godaddy>> #f59e0b
  BackgroundColor<<github>> #8b5cf6
  BorderColor #1e293b
}

title Deployment Architecture - gocaving.ai (Current)

node "Developer Workstation" {
  [VS Code]
  [Git Client]
  [WSL2/Ubuntu]
}

node "GitHub" <<github>> {
  artifact "Repository" {
    [index.html]
    [script.js]
    [assets/images/]
    [netlify.toml]
  }
  [GitHub Actions]
}

node "GoDaddy" <<godaddy>> {
  [DNS Server] {
    [A Record: 75.2.60.5]
    [CNAME: www]
  }
}

cloud "Netlify" <<netlify>> {
  node "Build System" {
    [Build Agent]
    [Deploy Pipeline]
  }

  node "Global CDN" {
    [Edge Node - US East]
    [Edge Node - US West]
    [Edge Node - Europe]
    [Edge Node - Asia]
  }

  node "Services" {
    [Forms Service]
    [SSL/TLS]
    [Analytics]
  }

  database "Form Storage" {
    [Submissions DB]
  }
}

' Deployment Flow
[VS Code] --> [Git Client] : Edit files
[Git Client] --> [Repository] : git push
[Repository] --> [GitHub Actions] : Trigger webhook
[GitHub Actions] --> [Build Agent] : Notify new commit
[Build Agent] --> [Repository] : Pull code
[Build Agent] --> [Deploy Pipeline] : Build & deploy
[Deploy Pipeline] --> [Edge Node - US East] : Distribute
[Deploy Pipeline] --> [Edge Node - US West] : Distribute
[Deploy Pipeline] --> [Edge Node - Europe] : Distribute
[Deploy Pipeline] --> [Edge Node - Asia] : Distribute

' User Access Flow
[DNS Server] --> [Edge Node - US East] : Resolve gocaving.ai
[Edge Node - US East] --> [SSL/TLS] : HTTPS connection
[Edge Node - US East] --> [Forms Service] : Form submissions
[Forms Service] --> [Submissions DB] : Store data

note right of [Build Agent]
  Build Process:
  1. Git clone repo
  2. Copy static files
  3. No build command (pure HTML)
  4. Deploy to CDN

  Deploy Time: 30-60 seconds
end note

note left of [DNS Server]
  DNS Configuration:

  Type: A
  Name: @
  Value: 75.2.60.5

  Type: CNAME
  Name: www
  Value: gocaving-ai.netlify.app
end note

note bottom of [Edge Node - US East]
  CDN Features:
  - Global distribution
  - Auto-scaling
  - DDoS protection
  - Asset caching
  - Instant invalidation
  - HTTP/2 & HTTP/3
end note

note right of [Forms Service]
  Form Processing:
  - Spam detection
  - Data validation
  - Email notifications
  - CSV export
  - 100 submissions/month (free)
end note

@enduml
